<h1>PART 3053 FORMS</h1>
<hr size="2" width="80%"><p><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P0_0">PART 3053 FORMS</a></p>

  <ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P11_403">Subpart 3053.1 General</a></li>

    <ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P12_425">3053.101 Requirements for use of forms.</a></li>

    <li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P14_589">3053.103 Exceptions.</a></li>

  </ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P16_789">Subpart 3053.2 Prescription of Forms</a></li>

      <ul><ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P17_825">3053.204-70 Administrative matters.</a></li>

      <li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P22_1307">3053.222-70 Application of labor laws to Government acquisitions.</a></li>

      <li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P25_1561">3053.227-70 Conveyance of invention rights acquired by the Government.</a></li>

      <li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P28_1862">3053.245-70 [Removed and Reserved]</a></li>

  </ul></ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P29_1896">Subpart 3053.3 Illustrations of Forms</a></li>

  <ul><li><a href="3053.html" name="LOC_P30_1933">3053.303 Agency forms.</a></li></ul></ul><hr size="2" width="80%"><!-- TRANSIT - TEXTBAR --><p align="center"><a name="P0_0"></a><b>PART 3053 FORMS</b></p>

<br><b>Subpart 3053.1 General</b>

<br>3053.101 Requirements for use of forms.

<br>3053.103 Exceptions.

<br><b>Subpart 3053.2 Prescription of Forms</b>

<br>3053-204-70 Administrative matters.

<br>3053.222-70 Application of labor laws to Government acquisitions.

<br>3053.227-70 Conveyance of invention rights acquired by the Government.

<br>3052.245-70 Contractor report of government property

<br><b>Subpart 3053.3 Illustrations of Forms</b>

<br>3053.303 Agency forms.

<p><a name="P11_403"></a><b>Subpart 3053.1 General</b></p>

<p><a name="P12_425"></a><b>3053.101 Requirements for use of forms.</b></p>

<p>Unless excepted, forms prescribed in (FAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .../Far/FAR53.doc. --><a href="../../far2afmcfars/fardfars/Far/53.html">part 53</a></u></font> and (HSAR) 48 CFR part 3053 are required for use by all Components.</p>

<p><a name="P14_589"></a><b>3053.103 Exceptions.</b></p>

<p>Requests for exceptions to forms contained in (FAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .../Far/FAR53.doc. --><a href="../../far2afmcfars/fardfars/Far/53.html">part 53</a></u></font> and to DHS forms in (HSAR) 48 CFR part 3053 shall be submitted, as prescribed in (FAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><a href="3053.html">53.103</a></u></font>, to the CPO.</p>

<p><a name="P16_789"></a><b>Subpart 3053.2 Prescription of Forms</b></p>

<p><a name="P17_825"></a><b>3053.204-70 Administrative matters.</b></p>

<p>The following forms are prescribed for use in the closeout of applicable contracts, as specified in (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3004.doc#s30044804570. --><a href="3004.html">3004.804-570</a></u></font>:</p>

<p>(a) DHS Form 700-1, Cumulative Claim and Reconciliation Statement. (See (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3004.doc#s30044804570. --><a href="3004.html">3004.804-570</a></u></font>(a)(3).) </p>

<p>(b) DHS Form 700-2, Contractor’s Assignment of Refunds, Rebates, Credits and Other Amounts. (See (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3004.doc#s30044804570. --><a href="3004.html">3004.804-570</a></u></font>(a)(2).) </p>

<p>(c) DHS Form 700-3, Contractor Release. (See (HSAR) 48 CFR<font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3004.doc#s30044804570. --><a href="3004.html"> 3004.804-570</a></u></font>(a)(1).)</p>

<p><a name="P22_1307"></a><b>3053.222-70 Application of labor laws to Government acquisitions.</b></p>

<p>The following form is prescribed for use in connection with the application of labor laws, as specified in (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3022.doc#s30224069. --><a href="3022.html">3022.406-9</a></u></font>:</p>

<p>DHS Form 700-04, Employee’s Claim for Wage Restitution.</p>

<p><a name="P25_1561"></a><b>3053.227-70 Conveyance of invention rights acquired by the Government.</b></p>

<p>The following form is prescribed for including a means for contractors to report inventions made in the course of contract performance, as specified in (HSAR) 48 CFR <font color="#0000ff"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .3027.doc#s30273054. --><a href="3027.html">3027.305-4</a></u></font>: </p>

<p>DD Form 882, Report of Inventions and Subcontracts.<b>  </b></p>

<p><a name="P28_1862"></a><b>3053.245-70 [Removed and Reserved]</b></p>

<p><a name="P29_1896"></a><b>Subpart 3053.3 Illustrations of Forms</b></p>

<p><a name="P30_1933"></a><b>3053.303 Agency forms.</b></p>

<p>This section illustrates agency-specified forms. To access these forms go to: <font color="#0000ff" size="+0"><u><!-- TRANSIT - HYPERLINK --><!-- .http://www.dhs.gov/. --><a href="http://www.dhs.gov/">http://www.dhs.gov</a></u></font> (under Business”, Acquisition Information) or https://dhsonline.dhs.gov/portal/jhtml/general/forms.jhmtl.</p>
